I"Ò<p>I recently rooted my Nexus 6P and, of course, instantly began searching for ‚Äúthe best ROM.‚Äù  As mentioned before, I‚Äôve been 
out of the root game for several years, but I‚Äôm going on the assumption that any ROM that still has an active thread on the XDA Developer 
Forums has a fairly prolific feature list.  Basically, theyre all probably pretty good and there are dozens to choose from.</p>

<p>My Personal Picks:</p>

