  <li>Fill out a <a href="http://goo.gl/forms/P6HndN4XUxKyyQeV2">Google Form for I/O Comparison</a></li>
  <li>Sharing this Blog - Obviously my data sheet is publicly shared for a reason.  However, please consider supporting my efforts by passing around anything you find useful or enjoyable on this site.</li>
</ul>
